Package game.data

Interface K

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Battle, Command, Dragon, DragonTreasure, Dungeon, Grenade, HealthPotion, Kitten, Monster, Player, PrintCollection, Room, SaltaPinnar, Sword, ValueManager
    public interface K
    Contains constant values used in the game. An attempt to centralize the data for swifter access and to avoid hardcoding values directly if possible.
